                        <p></p>
<p itemprop="description">
When a Jewish prince is betrayed and sent into slavery by a Roman friend, he regains his freedom and comes back for revenge.</p>
                        <p></p>
    <div class="txt-block" itemprop="director" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <h4 class="inline">Director:</h4>
<a href="/name/nm0943758/?ref_=tt_ov_dr" itemprop='url'><span class="itemprop" itemprop="name">William Wyler</span></a>
    </div>
