        <h2>Did You Know?</h2>
    <div id="trivia" class="txt-block">
        <h4>Trivia</h4>


One of the very few (and very expensive) 65mm cameras in the world was wrecked during the filming of the chariot race.        <a href="trivia?ref_=tt_trv_trv" class="nobr" >See more</a>  &raquo;
    </div>
                <hr />
     <div id="goofs"  class="txt-block">
        <h4>Goofs</h4>
When Ben-Hur's and Messala's chariots lock wheels, Messala's wheel shatters. In the shot of the overturning chariot, the wheel is intact.        <a href="trivia?tab=gf&ref_=tt_trv_gf" class="nobr" >See more</a>  &raquo;
    </div>   
                <hr />
    <div id="quotes" class="text-block">
        <h4>Quotes</h4>
<a href="/name/nm0000963/?ref_=tt_trv_qu" ><span class="character">Messala</span></a>:
Judah, tell me, did you-did you think about what I said yesterday?
<br /><a href="/name/nm0000032/?ref_=tt_trv_qu" ><span class="character">Judah Ben-Hur</span></a>:
Yes. I talked to a number of people already. Spoken against violence, against incidents. Most of the men I talked to agree with me.
<br /><a href="/name/nm0000963/?ref_=tt_trv_qu" ><span class="character">Messala</span></a>:
Most? Not all?
<br /><a href="/name/nm0000032/?ref_=tt_trv_qu" ><span class="character">Judah Ben-Hur</span></a>:
No, not all.
<br /><a href="/name/nm0000963/?ref_=tt_trv_qu" ><span class="character">Messala</span></a>:
Who does not agree?
<br /><a href="/name/nm0000032/?ref_=tt_trv_qu" ><span class="character">Judah Ben-Hur</span></a>:
Well, the resentful, the impatient.
<br /><a href="/name/nm0000963/?ref_=tt_trv_qu" ><span class="character">Messala</span></a>:
Who are they?
<br />[<span class="fine">pause</span>]
<br /><a href="/name/nm0000963/?ref_=tt_trv_qu" ><span class="character">Messala</span></a>:
Yes Judah. Who are they?
<br /><a href="/name/nm0000032/?ref_=tt_trv_qu" ><span class="character">Judah Ben-Hur</span></a>:
[<span class="fine">pause</span>]
Would I retain your friendship if I became an informer?
<br />                [...]<br />
        <a href="trivia?tab=qt&ref_=tt_trv_qu" class="nobr" >See more</a> &raquo;
    </div>
